<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #1e293b;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
      }
      .field {
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        padding: 15px 0;
      }
      .label {
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #64748b;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .text {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #334155;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f8fafc;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #94a3b8;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
      .social-link {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #6366f1;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 10px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>We've Received Your Message!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p class="text">Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
        <p class="text">
          Thank you for reaching out to <strong>Rangdhanu IT</strong>! We have
          received your inquiry regarding "<strong><%= subject %></strong>" and
          our team is already reviewing it.
        </p>

        <div class="field">
          <div class="label">Summary of Your Message</div>
          <div class="text">"<%= message %>"</div>
        </div>

        <p class="text">
          One of our experts will get back to you within 24-48 hours. In the
          meantime, feel free to explore our latest services or check out our
          portfolio.
        </p>

        <p class="text">
          Best Regards,<br /><strong>The Rangdhanu IT Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Stay connected with us:</p>
        <a href="https://rangdhanuit.com" class="social-link">Website</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link">Facebook</a>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px">
          &copy; 2026 Rangdhanu IT. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
